{"tid":1824286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳解僱西餅廠全部長期散工　美心：不評論市場傳聞","createTime":"2020-01-14T10:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T11:08:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fe16b19680fd79ba765499c8032e508ba5277cd2","tid":1824286,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/maxim-11_83Uaa_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmaxim-11_83Uaa_1200x0.png&h=373880a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上有 facebook 專頁引述消息指，美心昨日起裁減所有長期散工，並引述知情人士透露，銷量受到大減，「生產多於銷售」，故裁員節省開支。美心回覆《立場新聞》查詢時稱，不評論市場傳聞。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 專頁「家明」昨晚表示收到獨家消息，指美心西餅廠房昨日開始裁減所有長期散工。該帖稱，美心節省開支多時，僅僱用少量長工，並依靠長期散工維持日常運作。是次裁員意味著，「分店銷量受到重大影響，生產多於銷售」，需要縮減人手節省開支。<br />\n<br />\n美心集團創辦人伍沾德長女伍淑清，多次發表反對示威的言論，引起示威者不滿，集團旗下商店遂成破壞目標。「家明」專頁帖子又稱，「反送中」引發的社會運動以來，美心旗下受影響的商店一度多達71間，目前亦有至少有10多間分店無限期停業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/網傳解僱全部散工-美心-不評論市場傳聞/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%95%A3%E5%B7%A5-%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerh4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=40e0e1fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%95%A3%E5%B7%A5-%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E%2F&h=da33c5b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/網傳解僱全部散工-美心-不評論市場傳聞/</a>"},{"pid":"cd689d7f4d5f1553fce6468ff5ef3ada96a337e2","tid":1824286,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"長散零保障根本搵笨柒"},{"pid":"70d9ea9f5ef87f950fd459d3d197f62bd9aa2eee","tid":1824286,"uid":2429,"like"